videos.description: Florida State's Jonathan Isaac gets a block and finishes the play with a dunk at the other end.
videos.headline: Jonathan Isaac follows up a block with a 2-handed slam

videos.description: Miami's Kamari Murphy gets the assist on a Ja'Quan Newton dunk
videos.headline: Miami gets an open dunk in transition

videos.description: Miami's Ja'Quan Newton gets a steal that allows Davon Reed to get a dunk in transition.

videos.description: Florida State's Phil Cofer finishes the alley-oop pass from Dwayne Bacon with a powerful dunk to put Florida State ahead 70-50 over Miami.
videos.headline: Florida State's Cofer throws down a monster alley-oop slam
